{"tid":1460802,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【又係領隊】 有種人同藍絲一樣咁憎","createTime":"2019-08-13T04:55:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T16:24:27.000Z","uid":142452,"like":4,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"fd0e217b4411cc1a6c0ba77a5893fb99f50e27c8","tid":1460802,"uid":142452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T04:55:56.000Z","msg":"雖然我知都有好多依行既係同我地一樣會企出尼一齊抗爭 但每次見到依一班懶係關心香港 轉過頭 生於亂世 只識避世 既仆街就興過火屎 仲要講埋d嘔心既說話<br />\n<br />\n以下內容可能令人情緒不安<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OJf1KKE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOJf1KKE.png&h=cdb7f87c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5bGz4KF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5bGz4KF.jpg&h=9e3fd1ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n先講812當日 , 811咁大件事,條友仲係到因為飛唔到而表示好SAD而唔係因為香港有難而好SAD<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kB3bnwv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkB3bnwv.jpg&h=1156ed39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n721元朗黑夜, 當晚仲要好CHILL咁不問世事睇月亮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BMPU4Lh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBMPU4Lh.jpg&h=60ea3464&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CXaAPbZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCXaAPbZ.jpg&h=90b9a4c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eRnrVR0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeRnrVR0.jpg&h=3e584f00&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n727光復元朗你去左邊 係去左支持中共啊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/98vdATb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F98vdATb.png&h=97ab23fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n總結 我都知領隊依一行成日要飛 但依條友五毛到不得了,一毛都無 , 香港有事果幾日都係香港,但一次都無出過尼行街 , 其實唔行都算 重點係仲要話比全世界知你去左吃喝玩樂<br />\n<br />\n提外話 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong>"},{"pid":"c004011ca83f5f363e907a09fc716c0005e3d270","tid":1460802,